5:
Today's the last day of your
Halloween patrols?
10:
Yes! I worked so hard, and now it's
almost finally time...
15:
There you are! I finally found you,
Melmyna!
21:
Yeah, you probably wouldn't
remember me. I'm just one of many
guys you beat down before...
23:
Thanks to you, my life got turned
upside down! You gotta take
responsibility for this!
26:
Melmyna! Wait, Mistress! Please
stab me one more time! I'm
BEGGING YOU!
33:
I used to be nothing but a no good
thief back then.
34:
Spent my days wasting the days
away, trying to find some way to
pass the time...
36:
Everything changed when I met you,
Mistress!
42:
Is that all? Come on, you can still
fight! Just a liiiittle bit longer, please!
47:
You handled your spear with such
precision, making each thrust
painful but not deadly!
49:
But most importantly—you looked
down on me with absolute disgust
in your eyes! You awakened
something inside me that moment!
52:
Do we... have to sit here and listen to
this whole thing...
55:
So please, give me another good
stabbing!
58:
Th-this is the first time anyone's
asked me to hurt them...
61:
But for some reason, it makes me
happy!
67:
Yes! I-if you're really okay with me
doing it!
70:
I'm more than okay with it! This is the
greatest day of my life!
74: Um... I guess I'll just stab you here?
78: Why did we tag along too...
85: Wait, don't go! I want you to watch!
98: Yes, give me all you got!
111:
Is this it? Or are you saving the
intense stuff for last?
116:
I just don't feel anything when I do
this to you!
124:
What I'm really into is... the eyes of
people tainted by fear and anger...
127:
But the way you look at me is full of
expectation... It just isn't doing it for
me...
135:
...Sorry for getting my snot and tears
everywhere.
138:
N-no, I'm the one who's sorry... I
wasn't able to meet your
expectations...
140:
You don't need to apologize. Sure,
you weren't the one for me, but...
142:
I'm only on this path in the first place
because you introduced me to a
whole new world!
144: Thank you for opening my eyes!
147:
O-oh, I didn't really do much,
though...
149:
I was only d-doing what I wanted to
do.
152:
Ahaha, I guess that's true!
Well, I'm off!
158:
I'll b-be rooting for you! I hope you
find someone who'll stab you to your
heart's content!
162:
...Do we consider this... a happy
ending?
